sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Container, Header } from 'semantic-ui-react' import { Title } from '../components/Title' import { FinishedCard } from '../components/FinishedCard' export const Finished = () => { return ( <> <div className="ui container"> <Container fluid> <Header as='h2'>Checked off My List</Header> <p> Look at you go, you voracious beast, you! </p> <h3> You've checked __ books off your list! | You've read __ pages! </h3> </Container> <div style={{justifyContent: "center"}} > < FinishedCard style={{justifySelf: "center"}} /> < FinishedCard /> < FinishedCard /> < FinishedCard /> < FinishedCard /> </div> </div> </> ) }
